msgstr ""
":doc:`モザイクとメッセージを２つのアカウント間で送信するガイド <../transfer/sending-a-transfer-"
"transaction>` を完了している"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:49
msgid "Complete :doc:`creating a mosaic guide <../mosaic/creating-a-mosaic>`."
msgstr ":doc:`モザイクの作成  <../mosaic/creating-a-mosaic>` ガイドを完了している"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:50
msgid ""
"Complete :doc:`restricting mosaics transfers <restricting-mosaics-"
"transfers>`."
msgstr ":doc:`モザイク転送の制限 <restricting-mosaics-transfers>` ガイドを完了している"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:51
msgid ""
"Create :ref:`accounts <setup-creating-a-test-account>` to represent the "
"product and another one to repesent the company."
msgstr "製品ともう一つの会社を表現する :ref:`アカウント <setup-creating-a-test-account>` を作成します。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:52
msgid ""
"Load the product's account with enough |networkcurrency| to pay for the "
"transactions fees."
msgstr "製品のアカウントに手数料を支払うために十分な |networkcurrency| を入金してください。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:56
msgid "Method #01: Using the SDK"
msgstr "方法 #01: SDK を使用する"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:59
msgid "Blocking transactions by address"
msgstr "アドレスによるトランザクションのブロック"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:61
msgid ""
"An account can decide to receive transactions only from an allowed list of "
":doc:`addresses <../../concepts/account>`. Similarly, an account can specify"
" a blocked list of addresses to block transactions from."
msgstr ""
"アカウントは許可リストの :doc:`アドレス <../../concepts/account>` "
"からのみトランザクションを受信できるようにすることができます。同様にアカウントはトランザクションをブロックしたいアドレスのブロックリストを指定することもできます。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:64
msgid ""
"Allow and block restrictions are mutually exclusive per restriction type. In"
" other words, an account can only be configured to have either an allowed or"
" blocked list per type of restriction."
msgstr ""
"許可とブロック制限は制限タイプごとに相互に排他的です。つまり、アカウントは制限の種類ごとに許可リストまたはブロックリストのいずれかを持つようにしか構成できません。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:66
msgid ""
"By default, when there is no restriction set, all the accounts in the "
"network can announce transactions to the stated account."
msgstr "デフォルトでは、制限セットがない場合、ネットワーク内のすべてのアカウントが指定されたアカウントにトランザクションをアナウンスできます。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:68
msgid ""
"Returning to our previous example, let us imagine that you want to configure"
" the product account only to accept receiving transactions that come from "
"the company's account. You might take the following steps to do so:"
msgstr ""
"前の例に戻り、会社アカウントからの受信トランザクションのみを受け入れるように製品アカウントを構成するとします。これを行うには次の手順を実行します。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:71
msgid ""
"Define the company’s address ``TCVQ2R-XKJQKH-4RJZWG-"
"DARWJ6-V4J4W7-F4DGH6-ZFAB`` in a new variable."
msgstr ""
"会社アドレス ``TCVQ2R-XKJQKH-4RJZWG-DARWJ6-V4J4W7-F4DGH6-ZFAB`` を新しい変数に定義します。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:85
msgid ""
"2. Create an **AccountRestrictionTransaction**, with restrictionType "
"``AllowAddress``. Add to the company’s address from the previous step to the"
" allowed list."
msgstr ""
"2. 制限タイプ ``AllowAddress`` の **AccountRestrictionTransaction** "
"を作成してください。前ステップの会社の住所を許可リストに追加します。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:100
#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:161
#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:211
msgid "Sign and announce the transaction with the product's account."
msgstr "製品のアカウントでトランザクションへ署名してアナウンスをします。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:114
msgid ""
"Now, if you send a :doc:`TransferTransaction <../transfer/sending-a"
"-transfer-transaction>` from another account, you will get an error since "
"only ``TCVQ2R-XKJQKH-4RJZWG-DARWJ6-V4J4W7-F4DGH6-ZFAB`` is allowed to send "
"transactions to the product's account."
msgstr ""
"今や他のアカウントから :doc:`TransferTransaction <../transfer/sending-a-transfer-"
"transaction>` を送ると ``TCVQ2R-XKJQKH-4RJZWG-DARWJ6-V4J4W7-F4DGH6-ZFAB`` "
"だけが製品アカウントへのトランザクション送信が許可されているためエラーが発生します。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:117
msgid "Blocking transactions by mosaic id"
msgstr "MosaicID によるトランザクションのブロック"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:119
msgid ""
"Imagine that the account that represents the company owns the following "
"mosaics:"
msgstr "会社を表すアカウントが次のモザイクを所有しているとします:"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:121
msgid "``company.share``: represents shares of the company."
msgstr "``company.share``: 会社の株式を表現"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:122
msgid ""
"``company.quality.seal``: represents that the product has passed a quality "
"test."
msgstr "``company.quality.seal``: 製品の品質テストの合格を表現"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:123
msgid ""
"``company.safety.seal``: represents that the product has passed a safety "
"test."
msgstr "``company.safety.seal``: 製品の安全テストの合格を表現"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:125
msgid ""
"In this case, it might be useful if the product could only receive seals and"
" not company shares."
msgstr "この場合、製品はシールを受け取ることができるだけで、会社の株は受け取ることができないようにすることに役立ちます。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:127
msgid ""
"Thus, you could narrow the type of transactions that the product can receive"
" from the company's account through the use of negation. Instead of "
"specifically allowing the seals, the product can be set up to block "
"receiving transactions that contain ``company.share``. This is how it can be"
" done:"
msgstr ""
"したがって、否定を使用することで、製品が会社のアカウントから受け取ることができるトランザクションの種類を絞り込むことができます。シールを明確に許可する代わりに"
" ``company.share`` が含まれる受信トランザクションをブロックするように製品を設定できます。このようにします:"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:131
msgid ""
"1. Define the **AccountRestrictionModification**. Add the mosaic id you want"
" to block to the blocked list."
msgstr ""
"1. **AccountRestrictionModification** を定義します。``ブロックリスト`` "
"に追加したいモザイクIDを追加してください。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:146
msgid ""
"2. Create an **AccountRestrictionTransaction**, with restrictionType "
"``BlockMosaic``. Add to the array the modification created in the previous "
"step."
msgstr ""
"2. 制限タイプ ``BlockMosaic`` の **AccountRestrictionTransaction** "
"を作成してください。前の手順で作成した変更を配列に追加します。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:175
msgid ""
"If the process was successful, the product account can now only receive "
"transactions from the company's account that does not include any "
"``company.share`` mosaic."
msgstr ""
"プロセスが成功すると、製品アカウントは ``company.share`` "
"モザイクが含まれない会社アカウントからのトランザクションだけを受け取ることができます。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:178
msgid "Removing a restriction"
msgstr "制限の除去"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:180
msgid ""
"After the company sells the product to the final client, they want to remove"
" the condition that only allowed the company's account to send transactions "
"to the product. The account restrictions can be removed as easily as they "
"were set up:"
msgstr ""
"会社が最終顧客に商品を販売した後は、彼らは会社アカウントが商品にトランザクションを送信することのみを許可していたという条件を取り除きたいのです。アカウント制限は設定するのと同じくらい簡単に削除できます。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:182
msgid ""
"1. Define the **AccountRestrictionModification**. Remove from the allowed "
"list the company's address."
msgstr ""
"1. **AccountRestrictionModification** を定義します。``許可リスト`` から会社アドレスを削除します。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:197
msgid ""
"Create an **AccountRestrictionTransaction**, setting the type "
"``AllowAddress``. Add as well the modification created."
msgstr ""
"``AllowAddress`` タイプ を設定して **AccountRestrictionTransaction** "
"を作成します。作成した変更も追加します。"

#: ../../source/guides/restriction/preventing-spam-attacks-with-account-restrictions.rst:225
msgid ""
"After the transaction gets confirmed, you should be able to send "
"transactions from any account to the product's account again."
msgstr "トランザクションが承認された後に、あなたは再び任意のアカウントから製品アカウントにトランザクションを送ることができるはずです。"
